MarkAsRead
==========

Rails plugin to manage read/unread status of anything you need. Has great performance and needs only one additional table.


Example
=======

    email1 = Email.create!
    email2 = Email.create!
    
    Email.unread_by(current_user)
    # => [email1, email2]
    
    email1.mark_as_read! :for => current_user
    
    Email.unread_by(current_user)
    # => [email2]


Wheres the code?
================

Stay tuned, it's still in development...


